elections](/wiki/Indirect_election "Indirect election") in which voters in
each state cast ballots for a slate of electors of the [U.S. Electoral
College](/wiki/Electoral_College_\(United_States\) "Electoral College \(United
States\)") who pledge to vote for a specific political party's nominee for
President. _**Bolded indicates that the party won the national election that
year**_
